- After 60s of continuous work, post '⏳ 작업 중 — N분 경과 · <도구>' and edit every 30s
- Tool label from container_state (PreToolUse hook); Korean tool names
- toolInFlight also feeds the typing keepalive: heartbeat goes stale during
  long blocking tool calls, container_state covers the gap (bounded by
  declared timeout + slack / 10min default)
- Progress message deleted when the real answer is delivered (delete op
  added to chat-sdk-bridge; checkmark-edit fallback)
- Elapsed base resets on each delivery
